args: Xander and the prince's eventful journey was\nfinally reaching its end...
We should return to the castle soon.
But first, I have one more task to complete.
You have served me well during this\njourney, and I intend to see you rewarded!
Merely name a thing that you desire,\nand your king will see it done.
I don't need anything. I'm just glad we\nwere able to help so many people.
Humility may be a virtue, but there is\nno need for it here. Surely you must\nwant for something?
Speak, vassal! Your king seeks to\ncompensate you for your labor!
In that case, all I really want is for you\nto keep doing what you've been doing.
Just keep helping me. That's all I need.
Is there truly nothing you want from me,\nhowever small?
Look, I get where you're coming from,\nbut I really can't think of anything.
Look there! It's the traitorous prince!
You're not getting away this time,\ncriminal! We're taking you in!
Let's get out of here, Xander!
I beg your pardon? WHAT did you just call\n{player_name}?
No one calls my finest vassal a criminal!\nI'll not stand for it!
Never speak ill of my vassals again!\nDo you hear me?!
Still, while they may have fled now,\nthey'll likely return with numbers.
Then we should get back to the castle.
This has been an eventful journey indeed,\nbut you stuck by my side during it all.
And all this time, I have been struggling to\ndecide on a worthy gift for you—but I have\nfinally thought of one.
It's nice of you to put so much thought\ninto it, Xander. What did you decide?
Ha HA! Prepare to be astounded!
Your reward shall be...this entire land!
If you rule this land, no one will name you\n＂criminal＂ again.
To date, I have simply been lending you\nmy strength—but from now on, I shall rise\nup and make you the supreme ruler of all!
Our conquest is only just beginning!
I'm glad you're willing to do this for me,\nbut ＂supreme ruler of all＂ seems\nlike...overkill?
Not at all! You are more than capable\nof it; you should realize that potential.
This journey has allowed me to discover\nanew that so long as I am with you,\nno dream is out of reach!
Of course, supreme or not, I will still stand\nabove you as the kingliest of kings!\nHa HA! Ha HA ha ha ha ha!
Heh. That figures. Still, it's reassuring\nto hear you say all that.
Thanks, Xander. I'll be counting on you.
An excellent response, my vassal!\nYou are not my finest for nothing.
Now let this continent be filled with our\ncries of Happy Dragonyule!
Our future is most bright indeed,\n{player_name}!
